- Legal department: please perform compliance review and provide any required edits. If legal requires changes, please return edits to HR for implementation in this draft.

If you have any questions about these terms, please contact HR or your reporting manager.

We look forward to working with you.

Sincerely,

Omninuera  
HR Team

